title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 11: WJC, Blackhawks, Leafs & More
description:
In this episode, the fellas discuss the Artemi Panarin deal, the World Juniors, and the resurgent Leafs before taking questions and checking in on segments.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
